1. Installation instruction:
	- Install Python 2.6+
	- Install a non-standard Python library:
		psutil
	- Install third-party packages:
		Graphviz
		sqlite3
		MySQL
	- Configure mDAG using web2py server:
		- Copy entire directopry into "applications" directory of web2py distribution
		- See webpy.com
	- Configure mDAG using Apache:
		- 
		- 
	- More information:
	   	- Personal version (running on a Windows computer)
			- 
	   	- Group-sharing version (running on a Linux server)
			- 

2. File structure:
	\models
		db.py
		menu.py
	\database
		storage.db
		sql.log
		<db tables of the app>
	\views
		\default
			index.html
			data.html
			analyze.html
			results.html
			overview.html
			firstlevel.html
			pattern.html
			filteredgene.html
			filteredpatterns.html
			secondlevel.html
			metacluster.html
			dataset.html
			fcgraph.html
			user.html
		\others
			downloads.html
			help.html
			references.html
		appadmin.html
		<other standard web2py files>
	\controllers
		appadmin.py
		default.py
		others.py
	\modules
		Scheduler.py
		Executer.py
		Methods.py
		prettydate.py <third-party packages>
	\static
		\css
			base.css
			<other standard web2py files>
		\js
			jqBarGraph.js
			jquery.js
			sorttable.js
			<other standard web2py files>
		\downloads
		\images
		\results
		\sampledata
	<other standard web2py files>

3. Functionals:
	See the Help page of the app after installing
